In the jurisdiction of Ya ' an , which administers Lushan , 19 people were reported missing and more than 5 , 500 people were injured , the administration said . The quake - measured by the earthquake administration at magnitude - 7 . 0 and by the US Geological Survey at 6 . 6 - struck the steep hills of Lushan county shortly after 8 a . m ., when many people were at home , sleeping or having breakfast .